<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <style>
        .bg-slate-50 { background-color: #f8fafc; }
        .main-card { max-width: 500px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 40px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-family: sans-serif; }
        .btn-reset { display: inline-block; background-color: #e11d48; color: #ffffff !important; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 25px; }
        .warning { background: #fff1f2; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; color: #9f1239; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50">
    <div class="main-card">
        <h2 style="color: #0f172a; margin-top: 0;">Reset Your Password</h2>
        <p style="color: #475569;">Hello <%= name %>, we received a request to reset your PH Health Care password. Click the button below to proceed.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="<%= resetUrl %>" class="btn-reset">Reset Password</a>
        </div>

        <div class="warning">
            <strong>Security Note:</strong> This link will expire in 1 hour. If you did not request this, please ignore this email.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer" style="text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;">PH Health Care Security Team</div>
</body>
</html>